Package classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Check
    Check class represents one check made on a particular website at a precise date One check is characterized by : A unique id The HTTP Status Code returned by the header when checking the website The response time in milliseconds The id of the Website on which the check is made The date when the check is made
    Website
    Website class represents one website the user wants to monitorize One website is characterized by : A check Interval - it is given by the user in seconds - it tells us how often we do a check on a website A date - when the website was added in the monitoring system A unique id A String url - it must be an existing url
